{"tid":2026470,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"新手貓奴求意見","createTime":"2020-05-21T03:27:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T01:47:11.000Z","uid":36195,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"40752cc1eac21c45b8974f16d7501183b9b26609","tid":2026470,"uid":36195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T03:27:22.000Z","msg":"黎緊會接兩隻主子返屋企<br />\n本身淨係接一隻 <br />\n但佢哋知道要分開之後好似好唔開心<br />\n所以我朋友就建議我接晒兩隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係新手有啲緊張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢哋而家兩個月左右 <br />\n暫時決定係會餵半濕半乾<br />\n打算餵wellness core幼貓糧 <br />\n罐罐方面就買咗汪喵 wellness同埋thrive<br />\n如果係零食方面大家有冇邊隻推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋想細細個開始幫佢哋沖涼剪指甲洗耳仔<br />\n上網睇啲人建議大概六個月開始就可以試<br />\n巴絲們有冇經驗試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋佢哋未完全好識用貓砂盆<br />\n應該比佢哋自己慢慢摸索定係教佢地好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c21aff746720abfe0e5171425e6db93c7948d77","tid":2026470,"uid":223084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T03:28:37.000Z","msg":"男定女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7024fe0c171a5b0a7f977ab280003209d108b52","tid":2026470,"uid":49549,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T03:29:07.000Z","msg":"你示範一次貓砂盤點用佢地就識"},{"pid":"002ea7061809002ad4f91329ccbaf20fef7c8d65","tid":2026470,"uid":190144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T03:30:35.000Z","msg":"放佢哋啲便便落貓沙再比佢哋聞"},{"pid":"277fcf9a1ea1759f5eed907698e87f20fa27f10c","tid":2026470,"uid":54001,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T03:31:28.000Z","msg":"咁細個唔使食零食啦<br />\n你唔畀 佢唔知會有零食呢一回事"},{"pid":"2e99db4c032609184865896441ee146f6a8abe5c","tid":2026470,"uid":36195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"