21T04:04:40.000Z","msg":"我估我3/4個月就已經畀<br />\n不過係因為要氹食藥"},{"pid":"e77c63c4924b46b1b44983ee3a4e3aba342dcd90","tid":2026470,"uid":207763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T04:42:24.000Z","msg":"兩個月咁細隻嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我個隻個半月個陣嚟 將佢粒屎放咗入盤之後佢就識去貓砂盤屙 <br />\n而家兩個月都食緊汪喵 我比汪喵營養罐做主 <br />\n夜晚都會比wellness core乾糧佢當零食<br />\n有時都比下thrive 同seeds 嘅副食罐 打算佢大啲啲牙堅固啲先食多啲乾糧"},{"pid":"23170ea7068188937de9d9a1d5285da304dbdcf6","tid":2026470,"uid":36195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e77c63c4924b46b1b44983ee3a4e3aba342dcd90","tid":2026470,"uid":207763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T04:42:24.000Z","msg":"兩個月咁細隻嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我個隻個半月個陣嚟 將佢粒屎放咗入盤之後佢就識去貓砂盤屙 <br />\n而家兩個月都食緊汪喵 我比汪喵營養罐做主 <br />\n夜晚都會比wellness core乾糧佢當零食<br />\n有時都比下thrive 同seeds 嘅副食罐 打算佢大啲啲牙堅固啲先食多啲乾糧"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:57:42.000Z","msg":"張相係我friend啱啱執佢返嚟嗰陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實都唔完全知道佢係幾大 不過都仲未打得針<br />\n我都見啲人話最好細細個開始淨係食濕糧 <br />\n我可能會早晚食濕糧 如果出咗去返工中間就可能擺低啲乾糧俾佢做小食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f22df795eb7fbe0cb8f3280651d5aa82e470e213","tid":2026470,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23170ea7068188937de9d9a1d5285da304dbdcf6","tid":2026470,"uid":36195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e77c63c4924b46b1b44983ee3a4e3aba342dcd90","tid":2026470,"uid":207763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T04:42:24.000Z","msg":"兩個月咁細隻嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我個隻個半月個陣嚟 將佢粒屎放咗入盤之後佢就識去貓砂盤屙 <br />\n而家兩個月都食緊汪喵 我比汪喵營養罐做主 <br />\n夜晚都會比wellness core乾糧佢當零食<br />\n有時都比下thrive 同seeds 嘅副食罐 打算佢大啲啲牙堅固啲先食多啲乾糧"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:57:42.000Z","msg":"張相係我friend啱啱執佢返嚟嗰陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實都唔完全知道佢係幾大 不過都仲未打得針<br />\n我都見啲人話最好細細個開始淨係食濕糧 <br />\n我可能會早晚食濕糧 如果出咗去返工中間就可能擺低啲乾糧俾佢做小食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:07:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幾時先到我發動到技能"},{"pid":"a7df0c98da8f1f165fc15c8c3eca386e54afe8de","tid":2026470,"uid":354311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11d036c362c2d64017b7b7e07ba2789f29d7bef5","tid":2026470,"uid":36195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"277fcf9a1ea1759f5eed907698e87f20fa27f10c","tid":2026470,"uid":54001,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T03:31:28.000Z","msg":"咁細個唔使食零食啦<br />\n你唔畀 佢唔知會有零食呢一回事"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T03:33:54.000Z","msg":"因為我睇台灣啲blogger就話如果同佢哋練剪指甲最好俾啲零食佢獎下佢<br />\n如果唔比零食有冇其他好建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:19:23.000Z","msg":"都好，但最好由細開始畀佢哋習慣<br />\n我隻貓細嘅時候點都可以剪指甲<br />\n但係大個咗就唔鍾意俾人摸手腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最好俾佢哋諗到「剪指甲 = 有好處 （零食）」"},{"pid":"92769de2ed3bad315a1181606f7b5c9b0c02733f","tid":2026470,"uid":120564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T09:02:29.000Z","msg":"想比零食可以比凍乾零食<br />\n純粹係抽乾水既肉<br />\n汪喵有好多款可以揀下<br />\n我主子好鐘意<br />\n次次見到都貓衝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7be5c4d27861dd6475ad70c9552bf007c4929215","tid":2026470,"uid":261522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T09:12:58.000Z","msg":"個半月左右 應該學了用貓沙； 要剪指甲，要帶去打貓針杜蟲藥。"},{"pid":"cd8930e5ca0471149ce7cbdb94712db0be97e481","tid":2026470,"uid":308624,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T09:17:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p